units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p  p  p

read_data pristine.struct

pair_style ?pair_style?
pair_coeff * * ?potential? ?elements?

neighbor ?skin? bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes

log pristine.log
thermo_style custom step pe press
thermo 10

fix 1 all box/relax iso 0.0
min_style cg
minimize ?etol? ?ftol? ?maxiter? ?maxeval?

write_dump all custom pristine.dump id type x y z
write_dump all custom quench.dump id type x y z

reset_timestep 0

thermo 1
log energies.log
run 0